---
title: Easy Tex-Mex Pulled Pork Enchiladas with Grilled Cheddar Cheese & Sweetcorn
description: You're going to fall head over heels for our new pulled pork. With the long slow cooking already done, it's ready to roll in any recipe.
Try adding the juicy, tender meat to a saucy filling, rolling it up in tortillas and baking it with a cheesy crust. It's enchilada heaven!
